# Phase-53 RTL-BASELINES-1: baseline directory pinned in git.
#
# Per docs/runbooks/rtl-snapshots.md, the 8 baseline pngs (one per
# covered page) are operator-seeded on first run via:
#
#   A11Y_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000 npm run test:rtl:update
#
# Once seeded, the pngs land in this directory and the suite gates
# against them on every CI run.
